::Prowl::

Prowl looks at Iron Raptor, slightly surprised at the tone of her voice. He 
transforms back into robot mode, a wave on nausea sweeping over him.

Prowl walks to Iron Raptor and puts his hands aroung her, kissing her, "We'll 
have plenty of time later...," he says as he takes a step back, looking Iron 
Raptor over to make sure she was all right. The scrape on her cheek wasn't 
too serious. "Right now let's get back to base."

Prowl's eyes widen as he glances at his arm, which was now covered with Iron 
Raptor's mech fluid. He seriously hoped that his hug hadn't hurt her.

"You're injured!" He says, concern in his eyes and his voice, "Transform to 
beast mode."

He turns to Tritan, "We'll manage. Thanks for your help, though."
